Thor is BACK! After the events of Avengers Endgame our God of Thunder was left with no family and no direction.  Now he's hanging with the Guardians of The Galaxy, but can our "Strongest Avenger" find a meaning to his life? Unfortunately, he won't have much time for self-reflection as a there isa malicious force targeting and killing all the gods in the multiverse! With the help of Korg, Valkyrie, and a mysterious new female Thor, Odinson hopes to bring the thunder, love and balance to the galaxy and meaning to his life. Join us as we discuss the latest, polarizing entry into the MCU in this spoiler-filled Thor: Love and Thunder Review! Please leave us a review on [ITunes](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our [merchandise](http://www.teepublic.com/user/comicbookclique)! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [ComicBookClique.com](episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

